OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,FCampaigners have said they will fight
OL,8,Fproposals for 20 wind turbines on peat
OL,9,Fmoorland near the Yorkshire Dales.
OL,11,FThe scheme, which has been put forward
OL,12,Fby Fred Olsen Renewables, would be
OL,13,Fbuilt on land on the border between
OL,14,FNorth Yorkshire and County Durham.
OL,16,FIt would comprise of 200m high
OL,17,Fturbines near Stang Forest between
OL,18,FArkengarthdale and Teesdale., which
OL,19,Fobjectors say would be visible as far
OL,20,Faway as Saltburn on the coast.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
