PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,FAn action group was set up last year
OL,8,Fto fight the proposals.
OL,10,FThe company behind the scheme says it
OL,11,Fwould generate more than 100 mega
OL,12,Fwatts of energy - enough to power
OL,13,F81,000 homes and businesses and help
OL,14,Fthe UK to achieve energy security and
OL,15,Fits climate ambitions.
OL,17,FCampaigners argue the scheme will
OL,18,Fresult in the industrialisation of
OL,19,Fmoorland and destroy the natural
OL,20,Fbeauty of the area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,FSuzi Wilson, from Hope Moor Action,
OL,8,Fsaid: "You would be changing the whole
OL,9,Flandscape and you will see that from
OL,10,Ftravelling north up the A1, travelling
OL,11,Fsouth from the A1 from Newcastle.
OL,12,FYou'll have these huge turbines
OL,13,Fblighting the landscape.
OL,15,F"What is the point in having curlew
OL,16,Fnesting grounds that's totally
OL,17,Fprotected in the national park if a
OL,18,Ffew hundred metres away you have these
OL,19,Fhuge turbines?"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,FA public meeting is taking place on
OL,8,FMonday (23 February) to bring together
OL,9,Fthose concerned about the proposal.
OL,11,FThe firm behind the plans says it is
OL,12,Fat a very early stage, with the first
OL,13,Fstage of consultation due to take
OL,14,Fplace later this spring.
OL,16,FEarly stage surveys have taken place,
OL,17,Fwith further more detailed ones to
OL,18,Ftake place as the project develops.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
