PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,FKelly Wyness, Senior Project Manager
OL,8,Fat Fred. Olsen Renewables, said:
OL,9,F"We're at an early stage in developing
OL,10,Four proposals for Hope Moor Wind Farm.
OL,11,FFrom the outset, we've been aware of
OL,12,Fboth the sensitivities of the site and
OL,13,Fits genuine potential to contribute to
OL,14,FUK energy security. As with our
OL,15,Fprojects in Scotland, Hope Moor will
OL,16,Fdeliver new renewable power, support
OL,17,Flocal jobs and skills, and provide
OL,18,Ffunding for moorland and environmental
OL,19,Fstewardship, cultural heritage and
OL,20,Flocal communities.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772062285
OL,3,CCampaigners vow to fight to stop
OL,4,Cmoorland wind farm with 200m high
OL,5,Cturbines
OL,7,F"As we move forward, we're committed
OL,8,Fto shaping the project with the
OL,9,Fcommunity. In the spring, we'll share
OL,10,Four early plans as part of a first
OL,11,Fstage of public consultation, giving
OL,12,Fpeople the chance to see the
OL,13,Fproposals, ask questions, and help
OL,14,Finfluence how Hope Moor can deliver
OL,15,Ffor the community and the country as a
OL,16,Fwhole."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@GO]
